they sit for months of the time,

00:33:27.750 --> 00:33:29.130
this took several months,

00:33:29.130 --> 00:33:30.870
Fred Mollison in Philadelphia did this,

00:33:30.870 --> 00:33:32.410
removing the rock grain by grain.

00:33:32.410 --> 00:33:36.400
And here you can see after
about six or seven weeks,

00:33:36.400 --> 00:33:38.240
a top of a head was revealed.

00:33:38.240 --> 00:33:39.920
This is one orbit where an eye would be,

00:33:39.920 --> 00:33:41.630
this is another orbit
where an eye would be,

00:33:41.630 --> 00:33:44.120
looks like you're dealing
with the top of a flat head.

00:33:44.120 --> 00:33:45.010
A few more months go by,

00:33:45.010 --> 00:33:46.410
and this was starting to be exposed,

