Here's the socket on the shoulder,

00:38:04.590 --> 00:38:06.190
here's the ball on the humerus.

00:38:06.190 --> 00:38:08.040
And we can see from the detailed shape,

00:38:08.040 --> 00:38:10.450
what the likely and unlikely
patterns of kinematics,

00:38:10.450 --> 00:38:13.150
of motion of one bone on the
