00:53:28.250 --> 00:53:29.470
If you look at this change,

00:53:29.470 --> 00:53:31.630
if you look at creatures
both living and long dead,

00:53:31.630 --> 00:53:33.458
what you'd find is a wonderful series of

00:53:33.458 --> 00:53:36.480
creatures with transitional features

00:53:36.480 --> 00:53:40.180
between acorn worm and
fish and I should say,

00:53:40.180 --> 00:53:43.590
some of the most important
species in this transformation

00:53:43.590 --> 00:53:46.800
have just been discovered
in the last 30 years.

00:53:46.800 --> 00:53:47.640
You could say the same thing

00:53:47.640 --> 00:53:48.960
with any other great transformation.

